00:17:17.912 --> 00:17:19.205
[laughs]

00:17:19.247 --> 00:17:20.414
That Shion, right?

00:17:20.456 --> 00:17:22.291
She's such a thoughtful girl.

00:17:22.333 --> 00:17:25.586
