00:17:28.756 --> 00:17:30.841
I'm just worried she
may have caught something.

00:17:30.883 --> 00:17:32.593
I don't think it's anything
contagious,

00:17:32.635 --> 00:17:35.429
but someday I'm sure
you'll catch it too, Satoko.

00:17:35.471 --> 00:17:37.974
You've completely lost me.

00:17:44.814 --> 00:17:47.650
Now that I've eaten all
I wanna do is take a nap.

00:17:47.692 --> 00:17:48.734
So hey, Kei.

00:17:48.776 --> 00:17:51.279
You always eat all
your foods at lunch, right?

00:17:51.320 --> 00:17:53.239
Like not a
single grain of rice left?

00:17:53.281 --> 00:17:55.241
Well, someone took
the time to make it for me,

00:17:55.283 --> 00:17:56.784
it wouldn't be
right to waste it.

00:17:56.826 --> 00:17:58.369
It's kinda funny.

00:17:58.411 --> 00:18:01.163
