00:19:30.878 --> 00:19:34.048
How does Rena Ryugu seem to me.

00:19:36.884 --> 00:19:39.095
She can take the joke
a bit far sometimes,

00:19:39.136 --> 00:19:40.805
but she still has a kind heart.

00:19:40.846 --> 00:19:41.681
I guess basically

00:19:41.722 --> 00:19:43.891
she's everything you
could want in a girl.

00:19:43.933 --> 00:19:46.519
